## Common questions

### Why is AI optional?

AI features cost money to run. Rather than charging a monthly subscription, the app lets you bring your own API key from Google Gemini (free tier available), OpenAI, or Anthropic Claude. You pay only for what you use, billed directly by the AI provider — never by us.

### My data — where does it live?

All of your trips, items, photos, checklists, and documents stay on your device. We have no server. We never see your data.

### How do I share a trip with my partner / family?

Open the trip → gear icon (Settings) → "Trips Backup & Transfer" → "Export All Trips" → share via AirDrop. The recipient accepts the AirDrop prompt and the app auto-imports.

### Can I use the app without AI?

Yes. Every feature has a manual fallback. Without AI you can still log items by typing, create trips, build checklists, and assemble itineraries by hand.

